mention.text: Mr. King , who lives in New York
Kleines Requiem , '' set to Henryk Gorecki 's '' Little Requiem for a Polka , '' a peppy little polka
a busy , feisty sort of relay race for three men , who hand off solos to one another with a lot of attitude , and dance in mad parallel at the end
mirroring each other 's long , slim-lined movements
Shostakovich 's early piano and trumpet concerto
the blocklike shapes and colors used by Kazimir Malevich , the Russian painter
